measurements.description:
Three closely arranged flowers on one upright inflorescence;
	sepals medium lavender; 
	petals spatulate, slightly undulate and dentiuclate, medium lavender, close purple spotting on midrib;
	lip broadly flared, undulate and denticulate, lavender, strong purple triangular splash apically, white throat;
	column bulbous, white;
	substance very firm; texture matte.
